Package: loco
Type: Package
Title: LoCo - Local Correlation Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Tim Stohn
Maintainer: Tim Stohn <tim.stohn@yahoo.com>
Description: Quickly detect local correlation patterns between features in single-cell data. Instead of clustering the data and looking for correlations within every cluster \
             LoCo creates neighbourhoods of cells, looks for correlations within those neighbourhoods and filters correlations that change smoothly across the single-cell \
             space from neighbourhood to neighbourhood.
License: GPL-3.0 license
LinkingTo: Rcpp
Imports: Rcpp,ggplot2
SystemRequirements: C++17
RoxygenNote: 7.1.2